    <stitle>7 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS FULLER SERIES - INSTALL - COMPANION FLANGE</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="IDcomponent" graphiccount="2">
        <title>COMPANION FLANGE</title>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install the speedometer drive gear or spacer and yoke (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13025j1">Figure 191</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f13025j1" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g13025j1" filename="../figg13/G13025J1.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
            <caption>Figure 191. Install Speedometer Drive Gear or Spacer and Yoke</caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Lock the transmission by engaging the two mainshaft gears with sliding clutches (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13025j2">inset, Figure 192</hotlnk>). Install the output shaft stop nut and tighten to
                450 to 500 ft-lbs. (610 to 678 N&#183; m).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f13025j2" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g13025j2" filename="../figg13/G13025J2.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
            <caption>Figure 192. Lock Transmission and Install Output Shaft Stop Nut</caption>
        </figure>
    </svcproc>
